Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很想大哭一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論何時也不是孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遙遠的夢想在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將它找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把雙眼閉上便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在心中的一個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.88,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要害怕 現在是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要放棄 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓著夢想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,經常也和你一起向明天邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繼續前進 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想堅信著 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.71,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想向著天空大聲呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃燒著 in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.05,0:01:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡,為了打倒支配著遙遠星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又再一次成為救世主進行冒險旅程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星界山的第一星界是有趣的童話世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.57,0:01:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這裏我們要把令花盛開的星之風吹起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在瑪莊尼鎮把控制著牛群的肥明打倒後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們就向加拉查鎮進發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.41,0:02:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.35,0:02:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第五話\N肥豬戰車大賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,快點過來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?火美子,發現了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.78,0:02:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看,這附近有很多豬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.68,0:02:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的呢,放眼望去都是豬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.95,0:02:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厲害呢,不論是大是小都有很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.49,0:02:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部也肥肥白白,好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.04,0:02:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有市鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼巨大的圓圈是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.46,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖像奧林匹克的標誌,那個不會是星之風宮殿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閃開,閃開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才的是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔大叔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我什麼也還沒說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.39,0:03:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正你想我像剛才的豬那樣拉你走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之去那個鎮看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許會有什麼情報的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連鎮內也有這麼多豬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露,再走快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡的鋼鐵兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行,被追上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飄飄攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鋼鐵兵,救世主渡當你們對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.18,0:04:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟欺淩弱小,嘗嘗野牛武一郎流吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全是膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒受傷吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.56,0:04:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠大家我才能得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼那些鋼鐵兵要追你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.73,0:04:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.92,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的名字叫亞路迪米,這家夥叫柏加露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀呀,大叔的肚打鼓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.37,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,剛才的吵鬧令我更餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那隻豬也好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露不是食物,在這加拉查鎮內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露它們是神的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃了的話會遭天譴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.80,0:05:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是支配這第一星界的露易·瑪格西的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜把柏加露的同伴吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西的妻子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,令人懷疑呢(同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.94,0:05:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜最喜歡舉行奧林匹克比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.51,0:05:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,選中那隻豬就硬要它參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.25,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和自己的叫湯忠桑的豬,戰車比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.55,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼強的豬,普通的豬沒法和它比的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.09,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後哈蒂娜就把輸了的豬做成菜全部自己一個吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.63,0:05:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們一直生活在不知何時會到自己的豬的恐怖之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.66,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於也選到我的柏加露了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能饒恕!混帳可惡的哈蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.74,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟把豬肉一個獨佔,絕不能原諒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.53,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒是亞路迪米,請問你知道星之風宮殿在哪裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西好像住在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我不知道星之風宮殿在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是瑪格西一定會來看比賽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.94,0:06:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.82,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.84,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣比起去找星之風宮殿更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了這樣的話就立刻行動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.98,0:06:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,湯忠桑,那是用肌肉強化劑特製的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.49,0:06:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃了肌肉會變強,力量也會大增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.19,0:06:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比賽也不會輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果輸了的話,我會立刻吃了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最喜歡強的孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是純情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.90,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有鎮內的小孩要見哈蒂娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是來叫我把豬還給他吧,我現在來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.70,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,不要因為對方是女人而面紅起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說什麼?在下做事經常都很認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜大人駕到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.25,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,來了這麼多人,找我有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常美的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然變成這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是亞路迪米,在下接受這次比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是如果你輸了就請你離開這個鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.27,0:08:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真大口氣,那麼比賽在三日後舉行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好洗淨你的豬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我會整個煮來吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.96,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.34,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露,你再走快一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼,走得真慢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露那已是很努力地跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.72,0:08:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.20,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣子怎麼能在和哈蒂娜的比賽中勝出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.91,0:08:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比賽只是為了引露易·瑪格西出來的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.20,0:09:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們會在比賽開始前把他收拾的,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也去追渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔,快過來拉這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材!誰會替你拉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下不是豬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.25,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對呢,大叔從很久以前起就已是河馬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下不是豬也不是河馬,我已不能忍你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.07,0:09:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要捉住你打你屁股,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西還沒到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比賽不是快要開始了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花生這裏有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是花生,是瑪格西!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武一郎先生,就這樣讓比賽開始 柏加露就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明是為了引露易·瑪格西出來才參加比賽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.34,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵!露易·瑪格西什麼時候才來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的達令一向都不守時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到比賽完了才到也不出奇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有什麼好傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為不論怎樣輸的也是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好,真的要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.06,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位,要大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在奧林匹克比賽要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.67,0:10:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出場的選手是,哈蒂娜大人和湯忠桑組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.48,0:10:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對手是鎮內的小孩,亞路迪米和柏加露組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比賽和以前的路程一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.72,0:11:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,圍繞加拉查鎮一圈再返回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.86,0:11:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比賽由我把這手帕,放手至掉到地上時開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼準備…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了,露易·瑪格西還沒到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有法子可以延遲開始嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個我拿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得好,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了,這樣可以爭取多一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阻礙比賽,我們會抓住你好好教訓你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.44,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是因為這大叔把手帕丟掉我才拿去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.42,0:12:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是丟掉啊,你沒有聽剛才的說明嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然有聽但已經忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那手帕掉到地上的話,比賽就會開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於也開始了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,加油啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.24,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,雖然有點阻礙但比賽平安開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,領先的是哈蒂娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,後面的是相差很遠的亞路迪米選手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.21,0:12:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露,請你再努力點跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是要把我趕出這個鎮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.83,0:12:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜大人漂亮地突破了阻礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向第五個彎前進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.77,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一方面亞路迪米選手是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.38,0:13:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟還在第一個彎 好慢,非常的慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟說了出來,不要輸,柏加露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也跳過那斜坡給他們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?亞路迪米選手竟上不了那個斜坡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.97,0:13:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是太沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真沒用太沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下也看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露,振作點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,輸了這場比賽你就會被吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露,柏加露啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜大人已走出場外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟著請用螢光幕觀看哈蒂娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.14,0:14:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,這樣就用神奇飯團增加力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.81,0:14:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神奇飯團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.05,0:14:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位,加強力量的是哪個飯團還記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是,那麼大家一起說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鮭魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鮭魚,吃了這個就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柏加露,你吃這個看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.36,0:14:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧,柏加露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這到底是怎麼一回事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亞路迪米選手突然充滿了精力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪的家夥,實在是奇怪的家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.08,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪的家夥,實在是奇怪的家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.85,0:14:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,我也來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那東西有什麼用?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是豬豬丸,用這個去追渡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.07,0:15:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的,到底哪個家夥比較奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的,這是有史以來最無聊的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勝負現在才開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.69,0:15:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小朋友,你叫亞路迪米嗎?有點本事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是亞路迪米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.26,0:15:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主 渡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是那個渡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就這樣對付你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太卑鄙了,哈蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就這樣掉進那個深谷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.82,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算想停,但在神奇飯團的效力還沒失之前又停不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了,有那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星之西班牙舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.71,0:16:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星之西班牙舞是能控制動物的響板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.77,0:16:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,用這個停止哈蒂娜的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,用那個把豬停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.26,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,豬先生,豬先生 停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,豬先生,豬先生 團團轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,火美子,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.04,0:16:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,豬先生,豬先生 向前又向後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.18,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有趣有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.78,0:17:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.82,0:17:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟戲弄我,讓你們知道會有什麼後果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔神,維納斯騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.10,0:17:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟叫出那廢鐵魔神出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我一起收拾你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會這麼簡單被你收拾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是嘴硬,完了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,用龍牙拳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈蒂娜,看來不能像玩戰國比賽時一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,達令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.18,0:18:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小鬼,竟要我親自出馬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.75,0:18:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一星界的波士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.74,0:18:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西就是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.16,0:18:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等,達令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.43,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你不要出手,這裏由我來解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.87,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得到,反正你快走開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是老樣子那麼愛逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了,我不會再出手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你,這樣才是我的達令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,小子 我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有對付她的方法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那岩石怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,總之飛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,哈蒂娜那家夥追來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,加速直衝過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是這樣會撞上那岩石的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題,我有方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,交給你了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.06,0:20:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真蠢,這樣去就會撞上岩石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.01,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是現在了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把翼垂直從隙縫中穿過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.00,0:20:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣連動也動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.71,0:20:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得好,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是機會了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.98,0:20:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.40,0:20:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,達令,我輸了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.24,0:20:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次到你了,和我決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.58,0:21:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是有精神的孩子,想和我決勝負的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.50,0:21:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就來東面超力布村的星之風宮殿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那時讓你好好享受一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,不用急!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥把地方告訴了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許會設了什麼陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.23,0:21:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對呢,現在最好慢慢和師傅計劃一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?說起來師傅怎樣了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.90,0:21:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西 快點來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.52,0:21:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠你們,我們可以放心地和柏加露它們一起生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.93,0:21:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是因為要把東面的超力布村露易·瑪格西打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是有這麼多豬,能做出多少人份的豬扒飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.47,0:21:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是想像不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.38,0:22:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,在下什麼也沒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,火美子 快點來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.12,0:22:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼… 拜拜了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.59,0:22:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見,保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.73,0:22:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,等等啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.30,0:22:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?這個胸口在驅跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.97,0:22:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop!已不能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.86,0:22:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連你也一個勁兒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.71,0:22:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油門不用放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.96,0:22:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直踏著 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.08,0:22:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.12,0:23:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為是速度的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,TONIGHT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.06,0:23:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.11,0:23:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能夠抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.21,0:23:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直望著的瞳孔湧上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.43,0:23:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.65,0:23:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今夜 MY LOVE
